summary: A conversion of the original Alicia CME preset with the right hair option and color. (I did not create her! Only a ECE to RM conversion!)
descriptionHtml:
DISCLAIMER

Alicia is not my creation. She is Lowgule's. (I probably butchered their name)
I simply converted the preset.

I was in love with the Alicia preset for so long that I actually gave up racemenu for ece.
For those who don't want to do that, I present to you, her preset, but made for racemenu.

I can't guarantee it's EXACTLY as it appears in the original, but I made it pretty darn close.

Requirements:

1. SG textures
2. SG eyebrows
3. Eyes of Beauty
4. Racemenu
author: Itstyle101
